<lb/>three. After scanning their faces he
<lb/>stood <metamark facs="#img_617_z002" rend="#HM _HMp" place="inline" function="caret" change="#StFa">^</metamark> <add facs="#img_617_z003" rend="caret _HMp" place="above" hand="#HM" change="#StFa">less</add> as <del facs="#img_617_z004" rend="single-stroke _ink1" hand="#HM" change="#StFa">one</del> mustering his thoughts for
